channel.title: Undetectable AutoTalker
channel.description:
The main reason I made this is because I got bored with tying things in world 2.It works very well for me and if you don't like it well I guess you can give me constructive criticism on how to make it better or things you would like to be added.
Edit: the picture is fucked. I made a mistake but w/e [img]http://img62.imageshack.us/img62/3058/atscreenydm7.jpg[/img] NewPic>> [img]http://img218.imageshack.us/img218/450/atscreenydt5.jpg[/img] When you press the start button. the script started typing the following. As you can see there is absolutely no pattern. This is what makes the script basically undetectable.! [code] cyan:shake:buyiing full guth 8m martin w flash3:shake:buying full guth 8000k martin w cyan:shake:buying full guth 8000k martin glow1:shake:buying full guth 8m martin w flash3:shake:buying full guth 8000k martin w glow2:shake:buyyin full guthan 8m martin w flash3:shake:buyyin full guth 8m martin glow2:shake:buying full guth 8m martin w purple:shake:buyiing full guthan 8000k martin w glow2:shake:buyin full guth 8000k martin cyan:shake:buying full guth 8m martin [/code]
[u][b]Credits to Mutant Squirtle for the typeSend and typeByte Function from SRL.[/b][/u]
After you download, I would really appreciate it if you could tell me how it went. If you were totally confused by the form. Please tell me. and ill try explain it a little better.
